@startuml
!include ../../styles/plantuml-theme.puml

top to bottom direction
title FIG-08-01. Online Store conceptual data model

skinparam linetype ortho

rectangle "Customer\n<<Concept>>" as Customer #FFFFFF
rectangle "Basket\n<<Concept>>" as Basket #F7F9FB
rectangle "Product\n<<Concept>>" as Product #F7F9FB
rectangle "Order\n<<Concept>>" as Order #F7F9FB
rectangle "Payment\n<<Concept>>" as Payment #F7F9FB
rectangle "Shipment\n<<Concept>>" as Shipment #F7F9FB

Customer -right-> Basket : owns
Customer -down-> Order : places
Basket -right-> Product : contains
Order -right-> Product : contains
Order -down-> Payment : paid by
Order -down-> Shipment : delivered by

note bottom
  Conceptual model only.
  It names business information concepts and relationships.
  It is not a database schema, API contract or process flow.
  Returns and support cases are outside this first view.
end note
@enduml
